        addSpecie.
        Adds a new specie to the humedal.
        pre: It has there must be space on the array of species to add a new specie.
        Parameters:
        nameSp, - the name of the specie.
        sciName, - the scientific name of the specie.
        migratory, - a number that indicates if the specie is migratory or no (1. for yes 2. for no).
        typeSP, - a number that indicates from which type is the specie (1. Earth flora 2. for Acuatic flora 3. for bird 4. for mammal 5. for acuatic animal).
        Returns:
        message, a message saying if the specie was added correctly.
